{"tid":2245470,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"遭警暴露宿者阿十「自殺」亡　9 停職警仍未被起訴　警方避答 9 人是否繼續支全薪","createTime":"2020-10-16T08:58:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T01:26:55.000Z","uid":56115,"like":6,"dislike":54,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"7fa77b5a501a6a8658892deb55368b4eb5597436","tid":2245470,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T08:58:02.000Z","msg":"警方今年 5 月就事件拘捕九名警員，涉嫌妨礙司法公正及刑事毀壞，警方昨晚回覆《立場》查詢證實，至今一直未有檢控涉事九警，九警仍停職候查，警方也未有回應九名警員停職期間是否支全薪。<br />\n<br />\n涉毆打曾健超被起訴的七警，在 2014 年 10 月 16 日被停職，被起訴前一直獲支全薪。《香港 01 》曾引述消息指出，七警在 2015 年 10 月被起訴後，警方根據七警的家庭財政狀況，以能確保維持生計為大前提下，警方未有「扣薪一半」，只扣月薪 10% 至 25 %。最終案中兩警員劉興沛及黃偉豪及後上訴得直，估計可重新獲發全額薪金。"},{"pid":"1c97957571f04b5cc447c0387400833732b832a1","tid":2245470,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T08:58:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E9%81%AD%E8%AD%A6%E6%9A%B4%E9%9C%B2%E5%AE%BF%E8%80%85%E9%98%BF%E5%8D%81-%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%BA-%E4%BA%A1-9-%E5%81%9C%E8%81%B7%E8%AD%A6%E4%BB%8D%E6%9C%AA%E8%A2%AB%E8%B5%B7%E8%A8%B4-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E9%81%BF%E7%AD%94-9-%E4%BA%BA%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E4%BB%8D%E6%94%AF%E5%85%A8%E8%96%AA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%259A%25B4%25E9%259C%25B2%25E5%25AE%25BF%25E8%2580%2585%25E9%2598%25BF%25E5%258D%2581-%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25AE%25BA-%25E4%25BA%25A1-9-%25E5%2581%259C%25E8%2581%25B7%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E4%25BB%258D%25E6%259C%25AA%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E8%25A8%25B4-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E9%2581%25BF%25E7%25AD%2594-9-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%2590%25A6%25E4%25BB%258D%25E6%2594%25AF%25E5%2585%25A8%25E8%2596%25AA%2F&d=Z58AETknIeTPCCdXMCOVUy2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=c53459ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%259A%25B4%25E9%259C%25B2%25E5%25AE%25BF%25E8%2580%2585%25E9%2598%25BF%25E5%258D%2581-%25E8%2